üîπ Flow now

1. In meetinglist1.aspx ‚Üí you click Start Meeting.

If Scheduled ‚Üí meeting status updated to Ongoing, redirect to meetingattendance.aspx?meetingId=123.

If already Ongoing ‚Üí alert confirms, then redirect without DB update.



2. On meetingattendance.aspx ‚Üí

It reads meetingId from query string.

Fetches Title + Start/End datetime from DB.

Displays them in your page.





